3148.Name: NJWPTL State Tournament 2021
3148.Details: The State Tournament will run COVID style this year.  The A, B, C, D divisions have been doubled this year. They will be A1, A2, B1, B2, C1, C2, D1 and D2. Each team will be placed into their division using combined team PTI.  EAch team is guaranteed 3 matches on Tuesday, March 9th and the winners of their 3rd match will play the Main, Cosolation, Reprieve or Last Chance Final on Tuesday, March 16th.  All matches will play a full 3 set format.
3148.RegistrationDetails: Registration will open at 2pm on Friday, March 19th.  The tournament is capped at 128 teams. 32/per division.  You will not request a division, your partner combined PTI will place you.  Cost of the tournament is $115/team (includes a $20 donation to the NJ Food Bank, favors, balls and prizes).

3153.Name: Championship Flight 2021 NJWPTL State Tournament
3153.Details: 8 team Championship Flight Tournament to be held at Canoe Brook Country Club. All matches will be 3 sets.  Due to COVID no food will be served.
3153.RegistrationDetails:
This tournament is invite only. Please do not register unless you have received an invitation email from the NJWPTL Board. Thank you.
Cost is $115/team- includes a $20 donation to the Community Food Bank of NJ

3373.Name: Beacon Hill Women's PTI 50+
3373.Details:
THIS TOURNAMENT HAS BEEN POSTPONED Canoe Brook Draw: Thursday January 13th MoCo Draw: Friday January 14th 50+ Draw: Friday January 14th

All players must have a PTI of 50 or higher. The draw will be limited to 16 teams. A waitlist will be opened once the draw has been filled. All teams will play 3 matches. All matches will be 2 sets, with a 10 point tiebreaker in lieu of a 3rd set. Lunch will be hosted at Beacon Hill Club in Summit, NJ. The tournament is currently full. Please register on the waitlist, we will pull teams off the waitlist in the order they sign up.
